#!ipxe
###
### ThoughtWave Kiosk — prepaidvdi.com
###
### Boots a minimal Debian ramdisk into fullscreen Chromium.
### Defaults to prepaidvdi.com; override with kiosk_url= kernel param.
###
### Usage from iPXE prompt:
###   chain https://boot.thoughtwave.com/kiosk.ipxe
###

:start
echo Loading ThoughtWave Kiosk...
chain https://boot.thoughtwave.com/kiosk.ipxe || goto custom_exit

:custom_exit
exit 0
